---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { config } from '../config';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import headshotImage from '../assets/images/site/engates_john.jpg';
---

<Layout title={`About - ${config.title}`} description="AI Researcher & Technology Innovator with 30+ years of experience">
	<section class="about-header">
		<h1>About John Engates</h1>
		<p class="subtitle">AI Researcher & Technology Innovator</p>
	</section>

	<article class="about-content">
		<div class="profile-section">
			<Image 
				src={headshotImage} 
				alt="John Engates - Professional headshot" 
				class="headshot"
				width={400}
				height={400}
				format="webp"
				quality={90}
			/>
			<div class="download-links">
				<a href={headshotImage.src} download class="download-btn">
					Download Headshot
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="bio-section">
			<h2>Current Focus</h2>
			<p>{config.author.bio}</p>

			<h2>Career Journey</h2>
			<p>As Field CTO at Cloudflare (2021-2025), I guided global enterprises through their AI and security transformations. Previously, as CTO at Rackspace for almost 18 years, I played a pivotal role in democratizing cloud computing. I helped bring "Fanatical Support" to life, building the culture and teams that set a new standard for customer service in tech. Under my leadership, Rackspace's Intensive Hosting division supported some of the Internet's most demanding workloads, including a little startup called YouTube.</p>

			<p>My knack for seeing around corners led to founding moments in open source infrastructure. When Frank Frankovsky reached out via Facebook message about "open sourcing cloud computing hardware," my immediate "yes" launched Rackspace's involvement in the Open Compute Project. I also led the RackLabs team that created the distributed storage system that became OpenStack Swift, now powering some of the largest storage platforms on Earth.</p>

			<h2>Notable Achievements</h2>
			<ul class="achievements-list">
				<li>Called to the White House to help rescue Healthcare.gov in 2013</li>
				<li>Testified before Congress on cloud computing's strategic value</li>
				<li>Founding contributor to OpenStack and Open Compute Project</li>
				<li>Named UTSA Alumnus of the Year in 2014</li>
				<li>Board member at Frost Bank (NYSE: CFR) and James Avery Craftsman</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Current Research</h2>
			<p>My current research explores the emergent behaviors and collective intelligence that arise when AI agents work together: a natural evolution from decades spent building the distributed systems that connect our world. I'm passionate about the transformative potential of multi-agent systems and their applications in reshaping how we work, create, and innovate.</p>

			<h2>Speaking & Mentorship</h2>
			<p>Throughout my career, I've been the translator between complex technology and business value, whether speaking at global conferences, advising boards, or mentoring the next generation through TechStars. I remain connected to UTSA through the College of Sciences Advancement Council and continue as an early-stage investor in cloud and SaaS startups.</p>

			<h2>Beyond Tech</h2>
			<p>I split my time between Texas (where I work) and Colorado (where I play), finding inspiration in both the tech ecosystems and mountain landscapes. When not pushing the boundaries of AI, you'll find me off-roading, cycling, snowboarding, or capturing it all through my photography.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="contact-section">
			<h2>Connect With Me</h2>
			<ul class="social-links">
				{config.social.linkedin && (
					<li><a href={config.social.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a></li>
				)}
				{config.social.twitter && (
					<li><a href={config.social.twitter} target="_blank" rel="noopener">X (Twitter)</a></li>
				)}
				{config.social.github && (
					<li><a href={config.social.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
				)}
				{config.social.email && (
					<li><a href={`mailto:${config.social.email}`}>Email</a></li>
				)}
			</ul>
		</div>
	</article>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-header {
		text-align: center;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6) 0;
		border-bottom: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.about-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.profile-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
	}

	.headshot {
		max-width: 400px;
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.download-links {
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
	}

	.download-btn {
		font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit)) calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 4px;
		display: inline-block;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}

	.download-btn:hover {
		background-color: var(--color-text-primary);
		text-decoration: none;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.bio-section h2 {
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
	}

	.bio-section p {
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.achievements-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
	}

	.achievements-list li {
		padding-left: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.achievements-list li::before {
		content: 'â–ª';
		position: absolute;
		left: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
	}

	.contact-section {
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.social-links {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		justify-content: center;
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
	}

	.social-links a {
		font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit)) calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
		display: inline-block;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}

	.social-links a:hover {
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: var(--color-background);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.headshot {
			max-width: 300px;
		}
	}
</style>